594
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:15,560
Well, newbie.

595
00:34:16,080 --> 00:34:16,680
Yes?

596
00:34:17,240 --> 00:34:20,240
Take this document to Khun Paga at the Accounting Department

597
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:20,960
