741
00:40:44,240 --> 00:40:46,520
What about the duty of boyfriend?

742
00:40:46,800 --> 00:40:49,080
If I can do this duty well

743
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:51,320
do you have a reward for me?

744
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:53,760
About this one,

745
00:40:53,960 --> 00:40:56,440
I have to think about it as well.

746
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:58,680
For this second reward,

747
00:40:59,680 --> 00:41:01,480
can I have…

748
00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:03,840
