761
00:41:44,120 --> 00:41:45,280
Okay, then.

762
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:46,480
I’m going to see May.

763
00:41:46,600 --> 00:41:48,080
Happy Valentine’s Day.

764
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:50,000
Happy Valentine’s Day.

765
00:41:50,160 --> 00:41:51,560
I’m going now. See you.

766
00:42:02,600 --> 00:42:04,800
you said you were busy.

