00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:08,200
I finished it early so that I could see you

768
00:42:10,240 --> 00:42:11,960
I have a gift for you.

769
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:15,600
I have a gift for you too.

770
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:25,680
Can I open it now?

771
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:27,000
No.

772
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:29,400
Open it when you are in your room

773
00:42:30,240 --> 00:42:33,920
But you can open my gift here

774
00:42:34,040 --> 00:42:35,440
Okay.

775
00:42:45,240 --> 00:42:46,680
